dc_title_s: Map of property of E.H. Hinners Sons and Estate of C.H. Meyer, Edgewater, N.J.
dc_description_s: Map showing the property lines indicating riparian rights of the company E.H. Hinners Sons and the estate of C.H. Meyer, Edgewater, New Jersey|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Lines of riparian rights as shown in full lines are as per map approved Jan 15, 1914 by Secretary of War|Dotted lines show grant from the State of New Jersey to Eide H.Hinners dated Feb. 14, 1895 and to Cord Henry Meyer dated May 24, 1893
